Sentencas: It has been found that electronic contribution to the total conductivity is higher than ionic contribution for all compositions.

Sentencas: The praseodymium doping with cerium dioxide introduces impurity bands within the ceria band gap and facilitates the electronic transition from valance band to conduction band through praseodymium impurity levels.
